**VAE**

- [qwen_image_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)


You can test and find the best setting by yourself. The following table is for reference.

| Model            | Steps | CFG |

IAMCCS QE Prompt Enhancer  Preset Summary
______________________________________________

 Camera Angles


Back View   camera positioned behind the subject

Front View   direct frontal perspective

Side View   clean lateral shot

Left 45   45-degree left-side framing

Right 45   45-degree right-side framing

90 Left   perfect left profile view

90 Right   perfect right profile view

Low Angle   shot from below for power or scale

High Angle   overhead shot for vulnerability

Worms Eye   extreme low ground-up shot

Birds Eye   top-down overhead perspective

Zoom Out   expanding frame, revealing environment

Zoom In   tightening focus on subject

Flip Scene   reverse camera orientation

Other Side   switch to the opposite direction

Behind Head   over-the-shoulder rear angle

Behind Back   following from behind during motion

Reverse View   mirrored point of view

3/4 View   three-quarter profile framing

Close Up   intimate facial or detail shot


 Style Effects


Photorealistic   enhance realism and lighting depth

Pencil Sketch   convert to hand-drawn pencil art

Line Art   clear black outlines and flat tone

Sepia Tone   warm vintage film look

Black & White   classic monochrome conversion

Add Colors   infuse vivid color into grayscale image

Enhance   general detail and clarity boost

Sharpen   accentuate edges and texture
